'''LAPACK'''，其名為'''L'''inear '''A'''lgebra '''PACK'''age的縮寫，是一以[[Fortran|Fortran]][[程式語言|程式語言]]寫的，用於[[數值計算|數值計算]]的[[函式集|函式集]]。
LAPACK提供了豐富的[[工具函式|工具函式]]，可用於諸如解多元[[線性方程式|線性方程式]]、[[線性系統|線性系統]]方程組的[[最小二乘法|最小平方]]解、計算[[特徵向量|特徵向量]]、用於計算[[矩陣|矩陣]][[QR分解|QR分解]]的[[豪斯霍德变换|Householder轉換]]、以及[[奇異值分解|奇異值分解]]等問題。 在[http://www.netlib.org/lapack95/ NetLib] {{Wayback|url=http://www.netlib.org/lapack95/ |date=20210113165850 }}亦提供了[[API|API]]經簡化的[[Fortran|Fortran]] 95版本的LAPACK95。LAPACK以[[BSD许可证|BSD授權]]的方法釋出。

==在其他编程语言中使用LAPACK==
很多现今的编程环境都支持C binding 库。LAPACK routines 可以在一定限制及约束下当作C 函数来用。
一些其他的[[language_binding|language binding]]也是可选的:

* [http://www.netlib.org/lapack95/ Lapack95] {{Wayback|url=http://www.netlib.org/lapack95/ |date=20210113165850 }} uses features of Fortran 95 to simplify the interface of the routines
* [http://www.netlib.org/clapack/ clapack] {{Wayback|url=http://www.netlib.org/clapack/ |date=20210126000423 }} for [[C语言|C]] (especially useful if there is no [[Fortran|Fortran]] compiler available, as it is already preprocessed with [[f2c|f2c]])
* [[LAPACK++|LAPACK++]] for [[C++|C++]]
* [[Armadillo_(C++_library)|Armadillo]] for [[C++|C++]]
* [http://www.netlib.org/java/f2j/ jlapack] {{Wayback|url=http://www.netlib.org/java/f2j/ |date=20210114124855 }} for [[Java|Java]]
*[http://www.dotnumerics.com/NumericalLibraries/LinearAlgebra/CSLapack/ CSLapack] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dotnumerics.com/NumericalLibraries/LinearAlgebra/CSLapack/ |date=20170716150201 }} for [[C_Sharp_(programming_language)|C#]]. CSLapack is the translation of Fortran to C# of the LAPACK numerical subroutines.
* [https://web.archive.org/web/20080818035500/http://www.ocaml.info/home/ocaml_sources.html#lacaml LACAML] for [[OCaml|OCaml]]
* Gonum/lapack is the translation of LAPACK and BLAS routines to Go (native)

